  "2026-06-25T04:55:07.059Z",codex-pm-ecosystem-audit-20260625,"Sub-agent evidence 2026-06-25T04:50Z: GitHub open PRs/issues none; Dependabot, secret scanning, code scanning, security advisories clean; latest main CI/Docs/CodeQL green on 99ede4f1. npm/GitHub latest v2026.6.24, with 9 commits after tag. Auto Release/Release latest visible runs on 2026-06-24 succeeded; no 2026-06-25 scheduled run visible yet. Nightly latest visible run failed on obsolete windows-latest/Node20; current matrix removes Node20 and GH #348 is closed, so verify next scheduled Nightly before closing pm-2kkl. Sentry gate currently fails on PM-CLI-1T, a fresh high unresolved handled ENOENT in pm stats history-stream reading; telemetry is healthy and remote backlog is 0. Recommend creating a PM-CLI-1T stats/history race issue under pm-34gb and updating pm-7zs0, pm-2kkl, and pm-rj3w with this evidence."
  "2026-06-25T05:16:08.445Z",codex-ecosystem-auditor,"Lane closure evidence: release/GitHub/Sentry/telemetry audit found GitHub baseline clean and Sentry PM-CLI-1T as the only release-gate blocker. pm-7o0s fixed and closed that race; Sentry/telemetry gate now passes required-mode with critical=0/high=0 and telemetry ok."
